Adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) zai yi tashin gwauron zabi a kasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya daga ranar 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Idan aka yi la'akari da yadda cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta bayyana a duk ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya, hakan na nuna cewa, duk da bambancin da ke tsakanin ƙasashe, cutar COVID-19 za ta iya yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da ya faru a Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa suna bukatar su kasance a shirye don karɓar ƙarin mutane da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman a cikin kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba, 2019, an samu mutane da dama da suka kamu da cutar numfashi a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa cutar ta samo asali ne daga wani sabon nau'in kwayar cutar coronavirus da yanzu ake kira cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida ta yanzu ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke dauke da COVID-19 suna da wasu cututtuka na rashin lafiya, kamar su cututtukan numfashi da kuma rashin numfashi, kuma yawancin su za su warke.
A cikin kashi 14 na cutar COVID-19 ana samun ta ne daga rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke bukatar asibiti, kuma kashi 6 na cutar na da matukar ciwo wanda ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Matsakaicin mutuwar da ake samu daga asibitocin COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, za mu bincika yanayin da ake samu a duk jihohin Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya da kuma kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Za mu kuma kwatanta adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Birtaniya da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu mutane da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya
Kamar yadda ya faru a China, COVID-19 ya bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe kuma cutar COVID-19 za ta bazu a wasu ƙasashe kamar yadda ta faru a China.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin rahoton 5 ga watan Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton mutanen Turai na farko da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 bisa ga bayanin da WHO ta bayar.
A cikin kasashen Turai/European Economic Area, an samu mutane uku da suka fara kamuwa da cutar a Faransa a ranar 24 ga watan Janairun 2020 wadanda suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, akwai wasu cututtuka na COVID-19 a cikin kasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma Burtaniya, kuma tun daga ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu mutum 39,768 da suka kamu da cutar da kuma mutane 1,727 da suka mutu, da kuma mutane 17,750 da suka kamu da cutar a Italiya kadai da kuma mutane 1,441 da suka mutu.
Samun cikakken adadin mutane da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ta sabunta adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar COVID-19 a kowace kasa, wanda aka samo daga tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatar lafiya ta kasa da kasa, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasa da na yanki da WHO, a kowace rana da karfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanin don kimanta yaduwar cutar COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya, kuma an kwatanta shi da Italiya.
Dangane da yanayin COVID-19, muna la'akari da matsakaicin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19, don haka muna lura da yanayin COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta Turai / EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma ba da jimillar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya
A cikin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da Burtaniya, za a bi tsarin da aka yi a lardin Hubei na China (Lambar 1).
A cikin ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya, cutar COVID-19 ta fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ta kai wani matsayi na musamman a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Sashe na gaba).
Ya dogara ne da yawan kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma a duk ƙasashen Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 ya yi girma daidai (Sarin bayani).
Lambar 2 ta nuna adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga watan Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Birtaniya suna da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar kamar yadda Italiya ta samu makonni 3 ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 zai yi tashin gwauron zabi a kasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Birtaniya.
Bayanan da aka samu a kan yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar za ta iya yaduwa a wasu ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da cewa akwai bambancin matakin da ake samu a cikin ƙasashe, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da kuma ma'anar cutar a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, da kuma bambancin dokoki da suka shafi zaɓin marasa lafiya da za a gwada su don gano cutar COVID-19, har ma da gwajin da aka yi bayan haka.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitocin Italiya a yankunan da cutar ta bulla sun ce kashi 10 cikin 100 na masu cutar COVID-19 na bukatar kulawar gaggawa kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ce, asibitocin gaggawa na yankunan sun cika.
Bayanai na asibiti da/ko kulawar gaggawa na COVID-19 a yanzu haka suna cikin ƙasashen Turai/Ƙasar Tattalin Arziki na Turai na kashi 6% da 1 cikin ɗari na yawan jama'a (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Amma, ana bukatar a haɗa su sosai don a ƙara su cikin sabon rahoto da ke ɗauke da adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar da kuma waɗanda suka mutu.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna cewa a Turai, ana samun ci gaba sosai a kulawar gaggawa da kuma a asibitoci, inda a Jamus akwai asibitoci 29,2 a kowace mutum 100,000, kuma a Portugal akwai asibitoci 4.2 a kowace mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe suna iya samun ƙarancin ko kuma mafi ƙarancin ci gaban da Italiya ke da shi (12.5 na asibiti da kuma matsakaitan gadaje ga mutane 100,000 a 201011).
Shirya hanyoyin kula da marasa lafiya ya fi na likitoci, saboda kusan adadin duk ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da Burtaniya dangane da asibitocin COVID-19 da kuma a &gt; 90% na rashin gado a cikin kulawa mai mahimmanci an bayar da su a cikin sabon tsarin ECDC na shida don kimanta haɗarin COVID-19.
Saboda yawan masu cutar a wasu sassan Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Birtaniya, kuma ana amfani da asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa don kula da mutane a wani yanki, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da cututtuka da gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin wani yanki da ake kira Nomenclature of Information Level 2 (NUTS-2).
Abubuwan da suka faru a Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe na nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 za ta iya yaduwa cikin hanzari a ƙasashen Turai/European Economic Area da kuma Burtaniya.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa mai mahimmanci suna buƙatar shirya don amsawa idan akwai ƙarin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma yawan mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa, musamman a cikin kulawa mai mahimmanci, kamar yadda za a yi a yankunan Italiya inda cutar ta ɓarke.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken gaggawa na kwanan nan na ECDC, ana bukatar gaggawa, ingantacciyar hanya mai inganci don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2, ta hanyar kawar da hankali daga kamuwa da cutar da kuma rage farashin rigakafin; saboda sanin ainihin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ba zai taimaka wa masu yanke shawara ba kuma asibitoci ba za su sami lokacin fahimtarsa ba, yarda da shi, da kuma shirye-shiryen kulawa ba tare da an gwada shi ba.
Binciken na gaggawa ya kuma tattauna hanyoyin kiwon lafiya na jama'a da za a bi don rage yaduwar cutar.
Akwai karancin damar da kasashe ke da ita na kara sarrafa kokarin da suke yi na rage yaduwar cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma matsa lamba kan harkokin kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na wasu ƙasashen Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai za su ci gaba da samun ƙarin mutane da ke fama da cutar kuma za su bukaci a saka su a cikin kulawar gaggawa a cikin kwanaki da makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar kwayar cutar korona ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda ta samo asali daga cutar sankarar bargo mai saurin yaduwa (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta kashe sama da mutane 3,000 kuma ta yi sanadiyar kamuwa da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, wanda hakan ya sanya ta zama babbar barazana ga al'umma.
A cikin dangantaka da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wadda ta yi sanadiyyar dubban mutane da suka kamu da cutar SARS a 2003, ana iya cewa SARS-CoV-2 ta samo asali ne daga namomin kaza kuma tana da alamun cutar iri ɗaya da kuma hanyar kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, COVID-19 ba shi da ƙarfi sosai kuma ba ya kashe mutane kamar SARS amma yana da yaduwar yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma yana shafar maza fiye da mata.
Yayin da ake ci gaba da samun ƙarin bayanai game da cutar, wannan labarin yana da nufin samar da bayanai na kan lokaci da kuma bayyana ayyukan bincike na gaba a kan wannan batun.
Za mu tattauna muhimman abubuwa game da cututtuka, dalilin da ya sa mutane suke kamuwa da cutar, yadda ake ganewa, yadda ake warkar da su, yadda ake sanin cutar, da kuma yadda za a kāre kansa.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan labarin zai taimaka maka wajen ganewa da kuma magance wannan mummunar cuta.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga watan Janairun 2020 ya zama na musamman kuma wanda ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa, yayin da aka umarci su su zauna a waje a duk lokacin bikin da kuma tsawon makonni bayan haka saboda barkewar sabuwar cutar.
Kwayar cutar ta yi kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wadda ta zama cutar sankarar numfashi (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; amma Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ta haifar an kira ta da cutar CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Wannan annoba ta soma a birnin Wuhan na ƙasar Sin, kuma nan da nan ta yaɗu zuwa ƙasar Sin da kuma ƙasashe kusan 50 a faɗin duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, cutar ta yi sanadiyar kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sama da mutum 80,000, inda sama da mutane 40,000 suka warke kuma aka sallame su daga asibiti, yayin da sama da mutane 3,000 suka mutu.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 shine "magabcin duniya na farko" kuma zai iya zama mai tsanani fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu, mata sun wallafa sama da kasidu 200 kan COVID-19 ciki har da ilimin kwayar cuta, ilmin cututtuka, ilmin halitta, ganewar asali, da kuma maganin cutar, tun bayan da aka fara bayar da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 game da yadda cutar ke yaduwa a cikin al'umma.
Wannan talifin zai yi ƙoƙari ya ba da taƙaitaccen bayani game da bincike da ake yi game da wannan sabon abu da ke yaɗuwa da sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wani cuta da aka samu daga CoV, cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya ɓullo a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da yadda ake yaƙi da cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci.
An yi hasashen cewa CoVs ba su da hatsari sosai, musamman ma suna haifar da kamuwa da cutar sanyi a kashi 15 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen duniya 4.
Amma a wannan karni, mun fuskanci cututtukan CoVs masu saurin kamuwa da cutar, kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wadanda suka fara a kasar Sin a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma suka yadu cikin sauri zuwa wasu kasashe tare da kamuwa da cutar da kuma mutuwar mutane da yawa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine CoV na uku da ya bayyana a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin adadi. An fara gano kwayar cutar numfashi mai lamba 1.1, wacce ba a san asalin ta ba a Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Fabrairu, 2019 ta Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta China.
Bayan kwana bakwai sai aka gano yadda cutar ta CoV take.
A ranar 15 ga Janairu, 2020, an samu mutuwar mutum na farko a Wuhan.
A lokacin, cutar tana yaɗuwa da sauri zuwa birane, larduna, da kuma ƙasashe da ke kewaye.
A ranar 20 ga watan, an sanar da cewa an gano cutar, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa za a iya kwayar cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an rufe birnin Wuhan kuma an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, an fara binciken cutar, amma daga cikin mutane 41 da suka kamu da cutar, mutane 21 ne kawai suka isa kasuwar kifin teku ta Wuhan inda cutar ta samo asali daga wani dabba da ba a san inda ta fito ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cutar a matsayin barazana ga duniya.
A lokacin da muke rubuta wannan rahoto, cutar ta riga ta bazu a duk ƙasar Sin da kuma wasu ƙasashe kusan 50 a dukan duniya (Littafi.2).
Ba a san yadda za a yi gagarumin girgizar ba, ko kuma yadda za ta yi tsanani.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairun 2020, binciken da aka yi kan marasa lafiya 8,866, ciki har da 4,021 da ke da cutar COVID-19 ya nuna sabon bayani game da annobar kamar yadda ke ƙasa (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 na kamuwa da mutane a kowane zamani, amma yawanci yana kamuwa da mutanen da shekarunsu suka kai 30 zuwa 65.
Kusan rabin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar (47,7%) sun haura shekara 50, mafi ƙanƙanta kuma sun kasa shekara 20, kuma mutane 14 ne kawai suke da shekaru 10 ko ƙasa da haka.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi rinjayar maza (0.31 cikin 100,000) fiye da mata (0.27 cikin 100,000).
COVID-19 ya yadu a cikin al'ummomi musamman a Hubei da kewayenta.
COVID-19 ya ɗauki matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farkon zuwa ranar gano shi.
Matsakaicin lokacin da cutar ke aiki kafin a gano shi kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin tsawon lokaci daga farkon zuwa mutuwa kwanaki 9.5 ne (4,8-13).
Yawan haifuwa (R0) ya kai 3.77 (CI kashi 95%: 3.51-4.05), kuma canjin R0 ya kai 2.23-4.82.
Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin ranar 23 ga Janairu, wanda ya yi daidai da lokacin da aka yi amfani da sufuri a lokacin bikin bazara na kasar Sin.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya ya kai 1.44% (CI 95%: 1.10-1,86%), kuma canjin yawan mutuwar ya kai 3.06% (CI 95%: 2.02-4.59%).
Abubuwa uku na haɗarin COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60), da kuma numfashi mai ƙarfi.
