Yawancin bincike sun nuna cewa wanke hannu yana da inganci fiye da na'urar bushewa da ke da yawa.
A shekarar 2008, an gudanar da wani bincike a Jami'ar Westminster, London, wanda kamfanin samar da kayan bushewa na Turai Tissue Symposium ya bayar da tallafi, domin gano bambancin da ke tsakanin kayan bushewa, na'urar bushewa da na'urar bushewa ta zamani.
Bayan wanke hannu da bushewa da na'urar bushewa, adadin ƙwayoyin cuta ya ƙaru da kashi 194 cikin ɗari a yatsun hannu da kuma kashi 254 cikin ɗari a hannu.
Bayan wanke hannu da bushewa da na'urar bushewa, adadin ƙwayoyin cuta ya ƙaru zuwa kashi 42 cikin ɗari a yatsun hannu da kuma kashi 15 cikin ɗari a hannu.
