Angiotensin conversion enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne da ke cikin ƙwayoyin (membranes) huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da kuma jijiyoyi.
ACE2 yana hana aikin canza angiotensin zuwa enzyme (ACE) ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II da kuma kara yawan ang (((1-7) don sanya shi mai tasiri don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana taimakawa wajen shiga cikin kwayar cutar corona.
