Angiotensin converting enzyme 2 wani enzyme ne wanda ke dauke da sinadarin Zinx a jikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana da N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma C-terminal na ammoniya mai ɗauke da hanci.
ACE2 tana da nau'in membrane guda ɗaya na furotin, wanda aikinsa shi ne ya zama enzyme a waje da wasu ƙwayoyin halitta da kuma ƙwayoyin halitta.
Ana samun ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar halitta ta hanyar wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, bayan haka, ana fitar da furotin a cikin jini, sai kuma a cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin kwayoyin halitta da yawa: ACE2 yana ɗaure da ƙwayoyin halitta na ƙwayoyin cuta na alveolarenterocytes na nau'in II, ƙwayoyin cuta da ƙwayoyin endothelial da ƙwayoyin tsoka na ƙwayoyin cuta da ƙwayoyin cuta.
