Aikin farko na aCE2 shi ne aikin ACE.
ACE tana ɗaure hormone na angiotensin I zuwa vasoconstriction na angiotensin II.
ACE2 tana ɗaure da carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine a cikin angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) kuma tana cohydrolyze shi a cikin angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma tana iya ɗaure ga wasu peptides kamar su [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma tana daidaita hawan kwayar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki wanda ke dauke da SLC6A19 kuma ya kasance a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A cikin binciken sunadarai na transmembrane, ACE2 shine farkon hanyar shigar da kwayar cutar coronavirus, da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar COVID-19).
